b'Odoru Mowai-kun': b'The anime centers on a Moai statue named Mowai-kun who is gloomy every day because it lives a dull life where it just watches the beach and the sun from atop a hill on an island. But one day Mowai-kun grows arms, and starts to dance. The anime will air within the Oha-Suta program\'s "Kyara-Suta" corner.\n\n(Source: ANN)'
